Our patients have suffered
indescribable trauma

20:55.421 --> 20:58.664
from TV hosts
perpetuating the cycle of abuse

20:58.666 --> 21:00.240
handed down since the days

21:00.242 --> 21:02.485
of<i> The Mike Douglas Show.</i>

21:02.487 --> 21:05.154
We treat all aspects of PTSD--

21:05.156 --> 21:07.080
post talk show disorder--

21:07.082 --> 21:08.415
<i> compulsive fake laughter,</i>

21:08.417 --> 21:10.659
<i> guest cancellation</i>
<i> night terrors,</i>

21:10.661 --> 21:12.177
<i> long haul Kelly Ripas...</i>

21:12.179 --> 21:14.438
Lindsey, who are you talking to?

21:14.440 --> 21:15.681
The audience.

21:15.683 --> 21:17.166
I'm warming up the audience.

21:17.168 --> 21:18.985
It's all on the teleprompter!

21:19.854 --> 21:21.261
Why don't you just put this on

21:21.263 --> 21:22.855
for a "who wore it best"
segment?

21:22.857 --> 21:25.658
Mm! (chuckles)

21:29.530 --> 21:31.080
Shh!
